 First Head of House Nengi broke down in tears on Thursday while discussing her mom with other housemates during the sixth wager task. Nengi, who lost her mom at a tender age, couldn’t control her tears as she relieved some moments about her late mom. Speaking at the presentation, Nengi revealed her late mom was a fan of Big Brother Africa and would have auditioned for this year’s show.  “She felt she could have done better if she went to school and my mum was young at heart and had always wanted to audition for Big Brother Africa, BBA. ‘’I’m sure if she was alive she would have auditioned for BBNaija this year but I know she’s happy that I’m here. “Sometimes, I act drama about her and take solace in that.” a